\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec3n h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<p>\u2013 Qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch kh\u00e1ch thanh to\u00e1n b\u1eb1ng chuy\u1ec3n kho\u1ea3n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c ng\u00e2n h\u00e0ng ho\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ed9ng h\u1ee3p ph\u00e1p theo quy \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a ph\u00e1p lu\u1eadt. Gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb thanh to\u00e1n c\u0103n c\u1ee9 tr\u00ean h\u00f3a \u0111\u01a1n GTGT mua b\u00e1n gi\u1eefa c\u00f4ng ty v\u00e0 kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng.<\/p>\n<\/div>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch thanh to\u00e1n Nh\u1eb1m mang l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 thu\u1eadn ti\u1ec7n trong mua h\u00e0ng v\u00e0 thanh to\u00e1n, Th\u01b0\u01a1ng hi\u1ec7u n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t GOVI xin g\u1eedi t\u1edbi qu\u00fd kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh th\u1ee9c thanh to\u00e1n nh\u01b0 sau: Thanh to\u00e1n tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp b\u1eb1ng ti\u1ec1n m\u1eb7t \u2013 \u00c1p d\u1ee5ng: \u0111\u01a1n h\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1eb5n \u2013 Kh\u00e1ch h\u00e0ng thanh to\u00e1n cho&#8230;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":0,"parent":0,"menu_order":0,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","template":"","meta":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/171"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/page"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/1"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=171"}],"version-history":[{"count":2,"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/171\/revisions"}],"predecessor-version":[{"id":173,"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/pages\/171\/revisions\/173"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/noithat9.webtudong8giay.com\/wp-